'''''Churfürstliche Fuchsjagd''''', also known as '''''Die Fuchsjagd zur Kaiserzeit''''' or '''''Zeitgenössische Fuchsjagd''''',<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rhCFjIBeplIC&pg=PA106&lpg=PA106&dq#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Kaiserzeit und Moderne: ein Wegweiser durch Berlin |author1=Michael Bienert |author2=Elke Linda Buchholz |page=106 |website=Books.google.com |date= |accessdate=2016-09-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanderkrogt.net/statues/object.php?webpage=ST&record=debe058 |title=Berlin - Altgermanische Wisentjagd |website=Vanderkrogt.net |date=2013-08-10 |accessdate=2016-09-18}}</ref> is an outdoor 1904 sculpture by [[Wilhelm Haverkamp]], installed at [[Fasanerieallee]] in the [[Tiergarten (park)|Tiergarten]], [[Berlin]], Germany.

