th non-believers|newspaper=L'Osservatore Romano|edition=English weekly|location=Baltimore, MD|publisher=The Cathedral Foundation|publication-date=10 October 1968|page=6|issn=|url=https://www.ewtn.com/library/CURIA/PCIDNONB.HTM|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20000614101645/http://www.ewtn.com/library/CURIA/PCIDNONB.HTM|archive-date=14 June 2000|access-date=|via=Eternal Word Television Network}}</ref>
